<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF326A8DF8279DFD162FB617" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF326A8DF8279DFD162FB617" blockId="201.[2010,2605,2903,3330]" lastBlockId="201.[1397,2604,3332,3487]" pageId="201" pageNumber="963">
Subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF7719DFD16E1B0F7" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[2189,2273,2980,3013]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
; 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF6EF9DFC17A6B0F4" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1874" box="[2323,2470,2981,3014]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montivagus">montivagus</taxonomicName>
species group. Morphometric studies recently split 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF7D79DAE16FCB726" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1874" box="[2091,2300,3063,3092]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montivagus">M. montivagus</taxonomicName>
into M. borneoensis, M. federatus, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF7719A7D1751B70E" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1874" box="[2189,2385,3107,3133]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montivagus">M. montivagus</taxonomicName>
, and M. peyton. Specimens now included under recently described species 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF70C9A3217D7B7B8" box="[2288,2519,3177,3212]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="indochinensis">M. indochinensis</taxonomicName>
were also originallyidentified as 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF69D9AC91424B782" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1874" box="[2401,2596,3215,3249]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montivagus">M. montivagus</taxonomicName>
. There are no genetic data available for “true” 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF7C19AB91702B632" authorityName="Dobson" authorityYear="1874" box="[2109,2306,3295,3329]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montivagus">M. montivagus</taxonomicName>
, and its relationship to otherspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF326A8DF97E9B5E18D5B61A" authority="Kaup, 1829" box="[1666,1749,3335,3368]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Myotis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="201" pageNumber="963" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Myotis</taxonomicName>
is uncertain. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
